metadata.name: The Bird & Blue Flower
metadata.description:
This physical painting is Acrylic on paper.
It’s a love story between flower & bird.The bird is a symbol of lover ,who falls in love with flower and they get to each other here, unlike the most of the novels.
In this painting the bird comes from my mind. There is not a specific kind of bird. It’s just a symbol and my mental bird. you can see the bird is calm beside the flower.
I invite you to see these love story.
